ZAP cluster definition

The Matter Door Lock cluster definition under firmware/app/zap/
(door_lock.zap, door_lock.matter, and the generated/* artifacts) is
derived from the NCS Matter Door Lock sample's ZAP definition,
licensed under LicenseRef-Nordic-5-Clause. The cluster topology
(endpoints, clusters, attribute selection) follows the Matter
specification for the Door Lock device type and is the canonical,
interoperable representation used by Matter Door Lock implementations
across the ecosystem.
